Package ohos.ai.cv.sr

Class SisrConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.ai.cv.common.VisionConfiguration
      • ohos.ai.cv.sr.SisrConfiguration

  • public class SisrConfiguration
extends VisionConfiguration
    Sets basic parameters required for single image super-resolution (SISR).

    The basic parameters include the SISR scale factor and quality.

    Since:
    1
